(enableSFBOpt, power_leakage).explanation: Enabling store-to-load forwarding buffer optimization adds additional circuitry and transistors to the processor, which increases the static power consumption due to leakage currents in these extra components;

(enableSFBOpt, area_cell_area).explanation: Store-to-load forwarding buffer optimization requires additional hardware logic and buffer structures, which directly increases the total cell area needed for implementation;

(enableSFBOpt, nDCacheMSHRs).explanation: The number of data cache Miss Status Holding Registers is a structural parameter independent of store-to-load forwarding optimization features;
